    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Theory concerned with the relationships and mutual informing among disparate images of and references to other texts and works of visual art or architecture placed within a text or work of visual art or architecture.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
